Description:
FERAL x@thedolphinsamsterdam bring you the ultimate hot box session on Friday 24th October from 4:20pm.
Sandy Kletz invites some of the best bouncey, trancey and groove artists to smoke & mix your Friday evening away:
@elithestargurl
@nvrenoughtaria
@kanelevy @sandy_kletz

In this fast and interlinked world, everything that happens affects everything else. It implies that everything in our world is a consequence of cosmic connections…
This time we'r connecting with @relinquobeats from the @raveonsociety Crew! With his solid and driving mixes we wil create a connection who will bring you directly in outer Space!

Line Up

23:30 - 01:30
@stephanrausch.dj (@visionserpentrecords/ @ubootsound )

